All new Echo Show 5 (2nd Gen, 2021 release) - Smart speaker with 5.5" screen, crisp sound and Alexa (Black) : Amazon.in: Amazon Devices & Accessories  Echo Show 5 is a smart speaker with 5.5” screen and Alexa that can be operated by voice and can fit on your bedside or coffee table. Alexa speaks English & Hindi.    Hands-free music control: Stream millions of songs in your favorite language from Amazon Prime Music, Spotify, JioSaavn, Gaana, and Apple Music. Enjoy singing along with on screen lyrics from Amazon Prime Music.    Your personal entertainment corner: Watch your favorite movies and TV shows from Amazon Prime Video and Netflix.    Monitor your home remotely: Activate the built-in camera remotely to securely monitor your home using the Alexa app.    Get started with Smart home: Setup smart lights, plugs or cameras with Echo Show 5 and control your appliances using just voice.    Improved 2MP camera: Use the 2 MP camera to call friends and family who have the Alexa app or Echo Show devices. Use drop-in feature to check on your kids or parents – just like an intercom.    Manage your day better:Just ask Alexa to set reminders and timers. Watch the latest news or get weather updates while you are rushing through your daily chores.    Designed to protect your privacy : Comes with a mic off button and a built-in camera cover.   
